description: The Gucci Sandal Model D is a blend of sophistication and comfort for warm-weather days. Crafted from supple leather, these sandals offer a luxurious feel against your skin. The elegant beige color complements a wide range of outfits. Available in US size 7, these sandals provide a snug and comfortable fit. Elevate your summer wardrobe with this exquisite piece from the prestigious Gucci Boutique.
